No, as long as you keep the screen on.<br />If you turn the screen on for about one frame, palette RAM risk to degrade. If you do for about 2 frames, OAM will too. As long as the screen is on there is no problem.<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://forums.nesdev.com/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=38">Bregalad</a> — Mon May 08, 2006 11:52 am</p><hr />
